This \textbf{ASSine} target specification is initially derived from the \textbf{ASSinePendulum} specification. So readers being familiar with the \textbf{ASSinePendulum} architecture concepts and hardware building blocks will find most of them unchanged within this document.

This \textbf{ASSine} document represents and describes all features of the \textbf{ASSine} and is adequate as a standalone reference.

This release of the specification has the status of an target specification.